  "sections": [
    {
      "name": "Arboreal Sapling",
      "sections": [
        {
          "image": {
            "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png",
            "name": "Additional Lore",
            "type": "image"
          },
          "name": "Always Growing",
          "sidebar_heading": "Additional Lore",
          "sidebar_type": "additional_lore",
          "sources": [
            {
              "link": {
                "alt": "Pathfinder #201: Pactbreaker pg. 82",
                "aonid": 241,
                "game-obj": "Sources",
                "name": "Pathfinder #201: Pactbreaker pg. 82",
                "type": "link"
              },
              "name": "Pathfinder #201: Pactbreaker",
              "page": 82,
              "type": "source"
            }
          ],
          "subtype": "sidebar",
          "text": "An arboreal sapling gradually grows into a more powerful form, such as an arboreal warden, filling whatever niche suits its interests and environment. However, even centuries later, an arboreal can slowly reshape itself to fill a new role, such as a warden transforming into an arboreal regent after their predecessor's retirement.",
          "type": "section"
        }
      ],
      "sources": [
        {
          "link": {
            "alt": "Pathfinder #201: Pactbreaker pg. 82",
            "aonid": 241,
            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "Pathfinder #201: Pactbreaker pg. 82",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Pathfinder #201: Pactbreaker",
          "page": 82,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Young arboreals often appear lanky and uncoordinated. Their awkwardness belies their burgeoning strength and decades of natural studies.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
  "sources": [
    {
      "link": {
        "alt": "Pathfinder #201: Pactbreaker pg. 82",
        "aonid": 241,
        "game-obj": "Sources",
        "name": "Pathfinder #201: Pactbreaker pg. 82",
        "type": "link"
      },
      "name": "Pathfinder #201: Pactbreaker",
      "page": 82,
      "type": "source"
    }
  ],
